WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:59.020
Now I would like to call Ayesha Sadiq, who has got the first position

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:05.410
and on this achievement the college has given her a gold medal

00:01:55.500 --> 00:02:00.780
I have got a good job now, then what objection does aunt have now?

00:02:01.760 --> 00:02:06.700
she doesn't have any objection, and neither she is refusing to get me married to you

00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:10.090
she hasn't refused but she diverts the topic by making excuses

00:02:10.490 --> 00:02:14.150
sometimes next week or next month, how much more she is going to postpone it?

00:02:14.260 --> 00:02:16.620
try to understand, Talal

00:02:17.010 --> 00:02:20.660
she is helpless because of our circumstances &amp; situation

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:25.390
she is just asking for the time, maybe she finds some solution

00:02:25.480 --> 00:02:28.920
Bano do you know, waiting is no solution to any problem

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:32.330
my mother has grown tired of coming to your house again &amp; again

00:02:32.780 --> 00:02:35.720
and now when I ask her to visit your house, she gets annoyed

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:41.290
if you are feeling so bad then get married as per her will, I won't say anything

00:02:43.490 --> 00:02:45.840
will you be able to live without me?

00:02:47.710 --> 00:02:51.010
I feel scared of thinking about it

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:56.660
whenever I think about it, my heart stops beating

00:02:57.310 --> 00:03:01.760
that is why I'm asking you to think about us instead of your family for once

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:05.610
think about our future

00:03:08.510 --> 00:03:11.370
isn't me &amp; my love important for you?

00:03:11.610 --> 00:03:15.090
your love is the most important thing to me

00:03:15.730 --> 00:03:17.520
try to convince aunt

00:03:17.770 --> 00:03:22.000
believe me Talal, she doesn't want to separate us

00:03:22.390 --> 00:03:25.573
Bano look, aunt has to understand the fact that you are her daughter not son.

00:03:25.884 --> 00:03:28.737
and you cannot earn for her for lifetime

00:03:31.070 --> 00:03:34.890
you have uttered such bitter words so easily

00:03:38.870 --> 00:03:40.940
Bano, this is the reality

00:03:41.440 --> 00:03:44.200
I've become tired of waiting

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:48.410
I can wait for you all my life

00:03:48.670 --> 00:03:52.220
but my mother wants me to get married first

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:58.000
you tell me, shall I not respect my mother's wish being the elder son?

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:04.440
this time my mother will say "yes", I promise you

00:04:08.270 --> 00:04:11.410
Okay

00:04:44.850 --> 00:04:47.040
Kareem, is dad fine?
yes sir

00:04:47.090 --> 00:04:47.600
yes

00:04:47.700 --> 00:04:49.420
did he eat the food?
yes sir

00:04:49.450 --> 00:04:50.280
did you give him medicines?

00:04:50.380 --> 00:04:52.680
yes, I have given it as soon as you had left
then why did you call me?

00:04:52.740 --> 00:04:54.450
sir actually...

00:04:55.180 --> 00:04:58.100
what?
with him...

00:05:03.150 --> 00:05:05.390
what is with you?

00:05:05.780 --> 00:05:09.360
I was so worried man!

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:33.540
this is the reason I've called you here

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.720
why she came here?

00:06:13.700 --> 00:06:16.050
I've called Sadia

00:06:16.810 --> 00:06:18.530
for what?

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.690
have you forgotten what she did with us?

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:24.280
dear, the last remaining days of my life

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:27.740
I want to spend them by forgetting all the mistakes

00:06:27.970 --> 00:06:30.170
but there isn't any place for her in this house anymore

00:06:30.620 --> 00:06:33.780
and neither in our lives
ask her to go back

00:06:34.630 --> 00:06:38.150
dear, I had always wanted all of us to live together in our house

00:06:38.570 --> 00:06:41.680
presently, I want to see my complete family

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:44.590
you are talking about which family?

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:48.780
have you forgotten that our family can never get completed

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:54.740
I cannot see her around at all, specially around you.
Ask her to go back

00:06:55.100 --> 00:06:57.600
dear, she came here upon my insistence

00:06:58.190 --> 00:07:01.760
she is your mother &amp; forgive your mother

00:07:01.820 --> 00:07:04.160
I shall forgive her?

00:07:04.900 --> 00:07:07.010
you can forgive her

00:07:07.490 --> 00:07:09.010
but not me

00:07:09.640 --> 00:07:13.980
dear, I cannot see you living all alone
This is my last wish

00:07:14.010 --> 00:07:19.360
please stop talking about such things. Nothing will happen to you

00:07:20.240 --> 00:07:25.484
yesterday, I had word with doctor Shoaib &amp; he gave me some hope. We are going to America tomorrow,...

00:07:25.920 --> 00:07:33.600
dear, last time the doctors had already given me answer

00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:37.970
I cannot see you leaving me like this

00:07:38.410 --> 00:07:40.630
I will fight till my last breath

00:07:41.570 --> 00:07:43.570
be brave my son

00:07:44.440 --> 00:07:49.830
you have to compete these circumstances by being brave

00:07:50.670 --> 00:07:55.440
and a brave person always forgives

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:58.240
forgive your mother

00:07:59.300 --> 00:08:01.860
okay

00:08:04.500 --> 00:08:05.500
Mr. Basit...

00:08:05.580 --> 00:08:06.110
actually...

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:10.200
Mr. Imtiaz is here for the condolence

00:08:40.930 --> 00:08:43.610
I wasn't in Pakistan at that time when I got this news

00:08:43.810 --> 00:08:45.800
I felt so upset

00:08:46.190 --> 00:08:48.620
Salman was just like a brother to me

00:08:49.660 --> 00:08:52.940
even he use to consider you as his younger brother

00:08:53.410 --> 00:08:56.170
Salman wanted to change this friendship into a relation

00:08:56.690 --> 00:09:02.500
he was so happy when we met last time, he was thinking about Soha &amp; Basit's marriage

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:07.760
I told him that it is an important matter &amp; the children consent is very important

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:13.600
at that time I didn't knew that he is going to leave us like this

00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:17.840
after all, how did this happen all of a sudden?

00:09:18.400 --> 00:09:20.890
I don't know, brother Imtiaz

00:09:21.280 --> 00:09:24.700
he called me one month before his death

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:30.160
at that time he was on the last stage of cancer, he asked me to come back

00:09:30.740 --> 00:09:32.890
you did the right thing by coming here

00:09:33.520 --> 00:09:37.060
even Basit has become so alone after Salman's death

00:09:37.450 --> 00:09:40.470
yes

00:09:42.540 --> 00:09:43.430
Kareem

00:09:43.520 --> 00:09:45.120
yes sir

00:09:45.660 --> 00:09:47.650
ask him to meet me in the lounge

00:09:47.810 --> 00:09:49.490
Ok

00:10:11.460 --> 00:10:13.590
here you go Bobby

00:10:13.950 --> 00:10:17.510
if this formula of yours proved to be successful

00:10:17.690 --> 00:10:22.920
then understand that you have learnt how to fool your naive customers

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:31.660
hey, what is this?
Have some mercy on us, Bobby

00:10:31.730 --> 00:10:35.410
I don't purchase milk, turmeric &amp; gram flour to apply on the face

00:10:35.800 --> 00:10:41.700
sister, there is a rule for every business.
At first, one has to invest in order to make some profit

00:10:41.870 --> 00:10:43.910
we haven't got a benefit of a single penny

00:10:44.140 --> 00:10:50.430
if it would have been so easy to get fair complexion by these home remedies, then everyone would have become one

00:10:51.400 --> 00:10:55.610
oh sister, speak softly... I've got one customer with a lot of difficulty

00:10:55.690 --> 00:10:58.170
do you want her to runaway as well?

00:10:58.260 --> 00:10:59.630
I hope so

00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:01.540
don't hurt me, sister

00:11:01.870 --> 00:11:03.210
an orphan's curse is very effective

00:11:03.280 --> 00:11:06.700
oh God, how come I got trapped in these orphans

00:11:07.140 --> 00:11:11.420
do you remember, what my mother had said before her death

00:11:12.690 --> 00:11:14.520
Take care of my Bobby

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:21.490
Bobby, please forgive us. We are struggling to meet the house expenses, these hobbies of yours doesn't suit you

00:11:21.620 --> 00:11:24.230
and I cannot see my things getting wasted

00:11:25.690 --> 00:11:28.670
I haven't given the whole house things though

00:11:28.920 --> 00:11:32.780
If I do something to pacify my heart, so you find it waste

00:11:32.890 --> 00:11:37.440
when your own daughters go out of the house &amp; do anything as per their will

00:11:37.560 --> 00:11:39.300
but you haven't stopped them till date

00:11:39.420 --> 00:11:42.080
an unmarried sister-in-law is not less than a torment

00:11:42.130 --> 00:11:44.062
don't you worry at all

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:49.635
the day when my parlor starts making profit, I will pay you every single penny along with interest.

00:11:49.706 --> 00:11:52.435
Its my promise to you

00:11:54.580 --> 00:11:56.930
Coming...

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:01.760
greetings mom!

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:02.960
greetings to you too!

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:03.870
take this

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:07.580
uncle, thank you!

00:12:09.450 --> 00:12:10.210
did you get the salary?

00:12:10.620 --> 00:12:11.910
yes, I've got it

00:12:11.950 --> 00:12:16.977
thanks a lot my God, tomorrow is the last date for paying the bill and the landlord will also come

00:12:17.031 --> 00:12:19.680
Leave it, come...

00:12:40.020 --> 00:12:42.320
this is twenty five thousand rupees

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:43.960
twenty five thousand rupees only?

00:12:44.510 --> 00:12:46.400
where is the rest of the money?

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:51.360
I have bought this stuff of five thousand rupees &amp; I've kept ten thousand with me

00:12:52.160 --> 00:12:54.550
what will you do with ten thousand?

00:12:55.350 --> 00:12:58.300
why? can't I keep ten thousand from my salary?

00:12:58.370 --> 00:13:02.860
there is no need to signify, I know it very well why you took ten thousand

00:13:03.220 --> 00:13:07.360
the jeweler had called, you had gone there right?

00:13:08.120 --> 00:13:11.210
what was the need to pay him advance for the set?

00:13:11.670 --> 00:13:15.140
it is difficult to meet the ends here &amp; you want to wear a set

00:13:15.390 --> 00:13:16.970
I don't like to

00:13:17.030 --> 00:13:20.640
I'm doing it for you, if you will give a gold jewelry set then it will add to your respect

00:13:20.820 --> 00:13:23.320
one cannot fill their stomach with respect

00:13:23.730 --> 00:13:26.640
leave that respect which can be earned after starving

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:32.430
the inflation is rising on regular basis, and I get shortage of even ten rupees at the end of the month

00:13:32.460 --> 00:13:33.093
and here you are

00:13:33.137 --> 00:13:37.671
mom, as per our circumstances it is very important for us to save every single penny otherwise nothing will work out

00:13:37.800 --> 00:13:42.020
really! so what is all this? yes?

00:13:42.210 --> 00:13:47.560
this tissue, spray... this bottle. Why you did this extra expense?

00:13:47.920 --> 00:13:51.600
actually aunt Shamsa &amp; Talal are coming

00:13:51.750 --> 00:13:53.260
Okay

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:58.090
that is what I'm thinking that since when you have started to care a lot about us

00:13:58.580 --> 00:14:01.270
you have started to meet that dishonest person once again

00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:05.480
what is this, mom? Why do you get so annoyed after listening to his name? What is wrong with him?

00:14:05.540 --> 00:14:09.070
wrong? Should I respect those mother &amp; son duo

00:14:09.230 --> 00:14:13.600
Oh God they are in such a hurry for the marriage, as if the dooms day is going to come tomorrow

00:14:13.710 --> 00:14:19.230
they have been seeking my proposal from the past three years. Aunty is coming here upon Talal's insistence

00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:22.640
please mom, accept it this time

00:14:22.850 --> 00:14:26.340
it is wrong to make some one wait for so long

00:14:26.440 --> 00:14:29.760
wrong! yes yes... now you will find me wrong

00:14:29.790 --> 00:14:32.390
somebody has said the right thing, It is not the right time to keep your daughter unmarried

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:36.160
it was me who was crazy, who use to consider her daughters as her care taker

00:14:36.200 --> 00:14:39.360
here a twelve year old girl wanted a husband

00:14:39.390 --> 00:14:41.840
mom, I've become of 32 while working

00:14:41.990 --> 00:14:43.990
are you taunting me, huh?

00:14:44.400 --> 00:14:49.100
this was only left. Now you will taunt your mother about your salary

00:14:50.790 --> 00:14:55.270
True that, a daughter can never become a son

00:14:56.420 --> 00:14:58.950
Talal's mother is looking for other girls for his marriage

00:14:59.000 --> 00:15:03.020
let them find a witch then, but listen to me very carefully

00:15:03.160 --> 00:15:08.010
those people who run away by leaving their loved ones in difficult times, they never stay happy ever

00:15:08.290 --> 00:15:14.350
mom, I'm not running away by leaving anyone.
I will fulfill my responsibility whole heartedly

00:15:14.670 --> 00:15:20.320
mom... but if you refused this time then my promise will get broken

00:15:20.360 --> 00:15:24.400
you are so concerned about yourself, and what about our hopes that will break. You don't care about it at all

00:15:24.560 --> 00:15:27.640
it is Talal's love that he hadn't been disloyal to me till date

00:15:27.980 --> 00:15:31.750
otherwise, the way you've asked them to leave... nobody comes back

00:15:31.930 --> 00:15:35.370
a woman who always praises a man's love, usually commits sin

00:15:35.450 --> 00:15:37.466
there isn't any such thing like love

00:15:37.555 --> 00:15:41.751
it is just the betrayal of eyes &amp; heart

00:15:53.650 --> 00:15:55.950
nice shoes, when did you buy them?

00:15:56.070 --> 00:16:00.780
I had bought them on the day, when I went out with sister Bano

00:16:04.950 --> 00:16:05.850
Zoya

00:16:05.970 --> 00:16:09.420
don't stare at me, I am not scared of anyone

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:12.350
what if someone sees you, then?
why were you looking at him like that?

00:16:12.840 --> 00:16:14.090
then let it be

00:16:14.210 --> 00:16:17.520
and if he gets happy to see me smiling, then what is the harm in it?

00:16:17.570 --> 00:16:20.370
stop your non-sense
you are talking so loudly, he will hear it

00:16:20.600 --> 00:16:23.660
by the way, nobody becomes a lover if they load a phone's credit twice

00:16:23.800 --> 00:16:25.040
he has you number?

00:16:25.100 --> 00:16:30.240
yes, I gave him because I didn't had balance. Do you know, he loads hundred rupees every time

00:16:33.170 --> 00:16:34.880
look straight

00:16:35.740 --> 00:16:39.450
what are you looking at?
if you see the girls on the way, so you have got a right to annoy them?

00:16:39.590 --> 00:16:40.760
look over there

00:16:40.920 --> 00:16:45.300
I'm not annoying, I was just passing by... and saw Zoya

00:16:45.360 --> 00:16:49.240
don't you dare to take my sister's name from your filthy mouth, understood?

00:16:49.760 --> 00:16:51.680
you are scolding me for no reason, I...

00:16:51.710 --> 00:16:57.150
I will break your legs if I ever see you on this road again, understood?

00:16:57.440 --> 00:17:01.660
look over there... let me get you some load, come with me

00:17:04.680 --> 00:17:07.190
shall we go to the market today, this way we will do some shopping

00:17:07.230 --> 00:17:09.030
as if mom will take you

00:17:09.240 --> 00:17:10.280
let's ask her

00:17:10.480 --> 00:17:11.440
greetings...

00:17:11.490 --> 00:17:13.840
greetings to you too!
you guys got so late today

00:17:13.880 --> 00:17:17.440
I was in the college, but she got late in coming

00:17:18.160 --> 00:17:21.350
mom, actually the result got announced today

00:17:21.740 --> 00:17:24.070
so, I've done top

00:17:24.600 --> 00:17:26.410
I've got a gold medal

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:28.370
oh wow!

00:17:28.690 --> 00:17:31.830
is it of Gold?
heartiest congratulations to you

00:17:32.350 --> 00:17:33.610
thank you, aunty

00:17:33.890 --> 00:17:38.920
do you know, today the whole hall was clapping when they had announced my name.

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:44.570
Thanks to God that your college has give you something.
Otherwise, I had grown tired of paying your college fee

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:46.720
mom, you don't have to pay my fee anymore

00:17:46.800 --> 00:17:51.800
people who does top gets scholarship from college. So my masters will be done on scholarship

00:17:51.840 --> 00:17:56.650
there is no need to do masters
whatever you have done is enough

00:17:57.360 --> 00:17:58.160
what happen?

00:17:58.390 --> 00:17:59.840
what had to happen?

00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:02.480
now its your duty to take care of the responsibilities

00:18:02.740 --> 00:18:07.520
when elders don't take care of their responsibilities then the younger ones should take their duties

00:18:08.010 --> 00:18:09.730
what does it mean?

00:18:09.930 --> 00:18:12.390
you stay quiet! I'm talking to Ayesha

00:18:12.730 --> 00:18:15.550
mom... I have to do masters

00:18:15.600 --> 00:18:18.420
I've got a scholarship, I did a lot of hard work for it

00:18:18.530 --> 00:18:21.580
everyone does hard work for themselves, but who is thinking about this house?

00:18:21.650 --> 00:18:26.320
Bano is in a hurry to get married, you are after studies &amp; Zoya is of no use

00:18:26.400 --> 00:18:29.360
who will think about this house?

00:18:30.330 --> 00:18:32.080
did something happen in the house today?

00:18:32.180 --> 00:18:34.940
don't know

00:18:54.470 --> 00:18:55.950
Bano

00:18:56.430 --> 00:18:57.470
are you sleeping?

00:18:57.600 --> 00:19:00.080
can anyone sleep here in peace, in mom's presence?

00:19:00.680 --> 00:19:02.040
what happen?

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:06.030
she is so angry downstairs &amp; here you are upset

00:19:07.200 --> 00:19:10.720
Ayesha... try to explain her

00:19:10.890 --> 00:19:15.790
if not Talal's family then at least she shall say "yes" while thinking about my love

00:19:16.080 --> 00:19:17.790
why? Has brother Talal said something?

00:19:17.840 --> 00:19:20.240
he wants to bring his mom here

00:19:20.660 --> 00:19:25.610
nobody cares about the embarrassment I face while giving him justifications

00:19:26.320 --> 00:19:31.170
mom gets so angry after listening to his name, don't know what is the problem

00:19:33.410 --> 00:19:36.990
don't you worry, I will talk to her

00:19:37.910 --> 00:19:41.070
she fears that I will back off, and I'm selfish

00:19:41.480 --> 00:19:46.050
I'm telling her that I will take care of the house expense after my wedding. But No, she doesn't trust me

00:19:46.580 --> 00:19:50.780
once I will get the job then everything will be fine

00:19:51.780 --> 00:19:53.900
nothing will get fixed like this

00:19:54.180 --> 00:19:58.410
if mom will keep on refusing like this &amp; Talal got married to someone else then...

00:19:58.460 --> 00:20:01.250
nothing as such will happen, he won't do

00:20:01.600 --> 00:20:05.620
our mother is the only mother in this world, who doesn't want to wed off her daughters

00:20:05.690 --> 00:20:07.040
don't say this

00:20:07.170 --> 00:20:09.900
she will hear this &amp; get upset. Then she will become more angry

00:20:09.960 --> 00:20:11.630
she has to listen the truth

00:20:11.760 --> 00:20:14.770
it is not us, but every other person is saying who knows the circumstances of this house

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:17.530
it is us who have faced the sorrows after father's death

00:20:17.810 --> 00:20:22.770
we have faced a lot of deprivations, we stood by her side in every situation for what?

00:20:22.800 --> 00:20:27.250
so that we shall sacrifice our happiness?
today its me, &amp; tomorrow it will be you

00:20:27.840 --> 00:20:31.500
any one of us has to stay in this house as a son

00:20:31.810 --> 00:20:33.780
whether you become a son or a daughter

00:20:34.210 --> 00:20:36.010
our mother is business minded

00:20:36.250 --> 00:20:40.080
wherever she finds benefit, she makes a deal

00:20:40.840 --> 00:20:42.657
By the way don't you worry at all.

00:20:42.782 --> 00:20:47.573
I will not let you &amp; brother Talal get distant, you will get married

00:21:00.100 --> 00:21:03.660
because of their haste, we have to starve

00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:06.210
I will talk to her
absolutely not!

00:21:06.540 --> 00:21:10.870
nobody will talk to Bano about her proposal, especially not you aunt Bobby

00:21:11.390 --> 00:21:15.720
what have I said?
I'm just saying that Bano is naive

00:21:16.370 --> 00:21:18.760
she is not aware of a man's reality

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:23.480
presently she doesn't value her freedom &amp; tomorrow she is going to cry for it

00:21:23.650 --> 00:21:25.110
she will realize it

00:21:25.260 --> 00:21:28.750
at that time, when that vicious guy will restrict her by becoming her husband

00:21:28.800 --> 00:21:34.430
mom... when a person who is giving backs off, then a person taking it shall step back quietly

00:21:34.510 --> 00:21:38.550
Why? Don't I have any right on her?
I'm her mother, I've got complete right on her

00:21:38.620 --> 00:21:42.560
shall she leave her rights because of yours &amp; till when?

00:21:42.880 --> 00:21:47.160
don't know when the problems &amp; expenses of this house are going to end, so won't you get her married?

00:21:47.220 --> 00:21:49.940
there is not need to advocate her

00:21:50.480 --> 00:21:55.050
search for a job, when you will get a job then I will wed her off

00:21:55.180 --> 00:21:56.760
Fine!

00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:58.970
okay then, I'm searching for a job

00:21:59.120 --> 00:22:02.850
but till then nobody will talk to Bano about her proposal

00:22:03.180 --> 00:22:07.200
and everyone will meet brother Talal &amp; aunt Shamsa with respect

00:22:12.300 --> 00:22:14.450
so mom has kept this condition?

00:22:15.040 --> 00:22:18.190
Somehow I have to do the job

00:22:19.150 --> 00:22:23.360
No Ayesha, I won't let you do this

00:22:24.620 --> 00:22:26.280
first of all complete your education

00:22:26.320 --> 00:22:29.800
my education is completed, I've already got a degree

00:22:29.990 --> 00:22:33.710
Besides, I've to do something to come out of this situation

00:22:33.760 --> 00:22:34.390
Ayesha

00:22:34.400 --> 00:22:36.470
don't worry about it, I will handle

00:22:36.560 --> 00:22:40.210
Bano... I want to talk to you

00:22:41.560 --> 00:22:42.720
go ahead

00:22:42.810 --> 00:22:47.090
Bano look, a mother never wants anything bad for their children &amp; I'm not your enemy

00:22:47.250 --> 00:22:51.860
and you know this very well that you are the only bread winner of our family

00:22:52.030 --> 00:22:55.360
I just talked to you about it downstairs, and you've started this conversation once again

00:22:55.410 --> 00:22:57.600
stay quiet, I'm talking

00:22:59.520 --> 00:23:03.400
Bano look, this house is running because of your salary

00:23:03.750 --> 00:23:05.290
therefore, wait for few days

00:23:05.390 --> 00:23:06.880
you can get married once Ayesha gets a job.. .

00:23:06.920 --> 00:23:09.450
I'm not doing all this to annoy you intentionally

00:23:09.490 --> 00:23:10.980
then leave him

00:23:11.600 --> 00:23:14.760
there is no scarcity of men for a working woman

00:23:15.140 --> 00:23:20.290
you will get a rich man, who will not stop you for helping your mother &amp; sisters

00:23:20.550 --> 00:23:22.760
Talal himself is a small employee

00:23:22.950 --> 00:23:28.190
It is not easy to get a naive &amp; sincere guy like Talal. And he is not greedy

00:23:28.520 --> 00:23:33.900
mom, if Talal would have been greedy then he wouldn't have agreed to marry Bano while knowing our circumstances

00:23:33.980 --> 00:23:37.870
yes! and it is my salary, wherever I spend it. He doesn't have any concern with it

00:23:37.900 --> 00:23:39.870
all of these things look good before marriage

00:23:40.090 --> 00:23:45.680
mom, Bano has already done a lot. Now I will take care of her responsibilities

00:23:45.840 --> 00:23:49.320
and as soon as I will get the job, the house expense will be born by my salary

00:23:49.390 --> 00:23:54.060
go &amp; find a job, besides a wedding ceremony doesn't happen so easily

00:23:54.140 --> 00:23:56.060
one has to arrange some money for it as well

00:23:56.090 --> 00:23:58.260
don't take tension about it

00:23:58.690 --> 00:24:02.470
mom... we will do everything

00:24:02.590 --> 00:24:05.600
for God sake

00:24:56.670 --> 00:24:58.860
Ayesha Sadiq

00:24:59.360 --> 00:25:01.950
you've done simple graduation

00:25:02.370 --> 00:25:04.500
and you've got no job experience too

00:25:05.200 --> 00:25:06.720
can you work on a computer?

00:25:06.800 --> 00:25:12.680
yes I can, MS Word, Excel.... computer programming. I know everything

00:25:14.540 --> 00:25:18.590
Okay... We will give you a call

00:25:38.310 --> 00:25:39.590
its good to have you back, sir

00:25:39.670 --> 00:25:41.200
thank you!

00:25:41.550 --> 00:25:43.880
I've got a meeting with Shantex Fabrics in next 15 minutes

00:25:43.980 --> 00:25:45.620
Sir, are we doing the meeting with them?

00:25:45.670 --> 00:25:47.770
of course, we are doing it. All our paper work is ready

00:25:47.810 --> 00:25:50.640
but sir their payment is still not done, they are calling as well

00:25:50.690 --> 00:25:51.910
they haven't got their payment as of yet?

00:25:52.020 --> 00:25:53.540
No sir
but why?

00:25:54.160 --> 00:25:57.680
you know we have got no leather products in our raw stock

00:25:57.780 --> 00:25:58.400
yes sir

00:25:58.480 --> 00:26:00.290
so what, Jamal?

00:26:01.680 --> 00:26:02.580
get the file to my room

00:26:02.660 --> 00:26:05.190
Yes sir

00:26:05.860 --> 00:26:08.570
what! accounts got seized

00:26:08.860 --> 00:26:12.970
yes sir, I got to know it today after coming to the office that all the three accounts of our company got sealed

00:26:13.030 --> 00:26:14.310
but why?

00:26:14.380 --> 00:26:19.540
sir, I had called the bank. They told me to talk to our lawyer

00:26:30.740 --> 00:26:34.160
hello Uncle Mansoor, please come to my office

00:26:35.060 --> 00:26:40.160
sir, I suggest that presently we shall cancel our meeting with Shantex Fabrics

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:42.870
No, we cannot do this

00:26:43.840 --> 00:26:46.200
and this matter won't go out of this office

00:26:46.580 --> 00:26:48.610
payment will be arranged

00:26:49.130 --> 00:26:52.660
if this deal got canceled, then our company will get a bad impact

00:26:53.260 --> 00:26:54.850
and I can't afford that

00:26:55.180 --> 00:26:57.270
Ok sir

00:27:37.760 --> 00:27:39.840
yes please, how come you are here?

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:41.050
*greetings*

00:27:41.130 --> 00:27:45.560
actually you've placed an advertisement in the newspaper for a job

00:27:45.700 --> 00:27:49.520
for the receptionist
Oh Ok

00:27:51.950 --> 00:27:55.320
please sit

00:28:04.370 --> 00:28:09.360
I hereby give devise &amp; bequest all my properties whether movable or immovable

00:28:09.450 --> 00:28:14.240
whatsoever &amp; whosoever to my son, on a condition that he has to marry first

00:28:15.930 --> 00:28:22.010
according to your father's will, all these properties will be transferred in your name after your marriage

00:28:22.900 --> 00:28:28.590
but before that, in this factory, company &amp; in other matters

00:28:28.770 --> 00:28:32.430
you cannot take any decision by yourself

00:28:36.790 --> 00:28:39.840
by thinking what he did this?

00:28:40.900 --> 00:28:43.020
and how can he do this to me?

00:28:43.710 --> 00:28:45.840
if you think peacefully

00:28:46.220 --> 00:28:49.120
then it was you who had compelled Salman to do this

00:28:49.290 --> 00:28:51.350
you are against marriage

00:28:51.810 --> 00:28:54.640
to refuse getting marriage again &amp; again

00:28:54.880 --> 00:28:59.260
a father, who extremely loves his son

00:28:59.680 --> 00:29:03.760
how can he leave his son all alone on the support of his life only?

00:29:03.870 --> 00:29:07.120
but how come dad didn't differentiated between my personal &amp; business life?

00:29:07.220 --> 00:29:11.090
because every successful businessman's life has some purpose

00:29:11.430 --> 00:29:15.510
and in order to achieve that purpose, one should have someone's support

00:29:15.840 --> 00:29:17.670
a life partner

00:29:17.910 --> 00:29:19.740
you must have heard

00:29:19.950 --> 00:29:24.920
there is always a woman's hand behind the successful person

00:29:25.470 --> 00:29:28.560
but I don't accept any such thing

00:29:29.160 --> 00:29:32.280
you don't accept it but the world does

00:29:32.610 --> 00:29:34.860
and the world has witnessed it

00:29:34.970 --> 00:29:38.010
what do you mean, nothing can happen?

00:29:38.580 --> 00:29:40.860
I mean, is this a joke?

00:29:41.180 --> 00:29:45.600
all my business deals are pending, my years long hard work is at stake

00:29:45.680 --> 00:29:50.690
you're here with dad's will that if I won't get married then my accounts will remain seized, are you serious?

00:29:51.110 --> 00:29:54.450
I cannot do anything, Basit

00:29:54.800 --> 00:29:58.640
this is Salman's property

00:29:58.720 --> 00:30:02.980
Now how do you have to become its owner, it is his decision

00:30:03.190 --> 00:30:06.630
he can never see you becoming a machine like this

00:30:07.190 --> 00:30:09.400
listen to me, Mr. Mansoor

00:30:09.840 --> 00:30:12.140
this is my dad's legacy

00:30:12.590 --> 00:30:16.230
and I don't believe this marriage like rubbish, so please do something

00:30:16.300 --> 00:30:18.230
I cannot let my career ruin

00:30:18.530 --> 00:30:21.380
you are doing all of this for whom?

00:30:21.440 --> 00:30:23.600
for myself

00:30:23.760 --> 00:30:26.100
I'm doing it for myself

00:30:29.470 --> 00:30:32.730
and after you...

00:30:34.260 --> 00:30:39.190
all these properties will go in the trust?

00:30:39.770 --> 00:30:43.370
I don't care... Change the damn will

00:30:43.910 --> 00:30:46.710
I don't care, Change the damn will

00:30:47.340 --> 00:30:51.950
Basit look, don't teach me advocacy

00:30:52.240 --> 00:30:55.990
this is illegal, I cannot change this

00:30:56.080 --> 00:30:57.960
so what do you want?

00:30:58.450 --> 00:31:02.080
you have to change yourself

00:31:02.860 --> 00:31:06.320
look... I'm just like a father to you

00:31:06.750 --> 00:31:11.710
you've grown up in my hands, I won't give you a wrong suggestion

00:31:12.210 --> 00:31:14.470
get married

00:31:14.950 --> 00:31:19.190
with any girl, whom you know or like

00:31:19.290 --> 00:31:23.900
or either that girl, what was her name.... yes

00:31:24.210 --> 00:31:27.960
what about Imtiaz's daughter?
meet her, maybe your decision gets changed

00:31:28.020 --> 00:31:30.280
No!

00:31:31.460 --> 00:31:33.460
ok listen

00:31:33.690 --> 00:31:37.120
if you say so, then shall I look for a girl for you?

00:31:37.200 --> 00:31:39.210
what is it, Mr. Mansoor?

00:31:39.700 --> 00:31:43.470
have you opened a marriage bureau after leaving advocacy?

00:31:44.540 --> 00:31:48.860
if I have to do this for you, then I will do it

00:31:51.990 --> 00:31:55.200
if you can do anything for me

00:31:55.520 --> 00:31:58.940
then change this will

00:32:00.890 --> 00:32:02.970
dear...

00:32:05.370 --> 00:32:09.430
consider this will as a line on the stone

00:32:09.690 --> 00:32:12.940
rest is your choice

00:32:29.550 --> 00:32:31.800
so you are the new receptionist

00:32:32.150 --> 00:32:34.120
I like it

00:32:34.640 --> 00:32:37.600
I hope you are not in a hurry to leave

00:32:40.600 --> 00:32:43.400
alright then, let's talk about the money

00:32:43.670 --> 00:32:44.820
how much money do you want?

00:32:44.910 --> 00:32:49.470
sir.... presently, I don't have any demand for the salary

00:32:49.930 --> 00:32:51.270
what are you doing?

00:32:51.510 --> 00:32:54.750
sorry! I clicked it accidentally &amp; the camera was open

00:32:54.880 --> 00:32:55.940
delete it

00:32:56.030 --> 00:33:00.440
hey! what is the hurry
look, how pretty you are looking

00:33:00.900 --> 00:33:03.760
isn't this a disgusting way to get free with someone?

00:33:05.050 --> 00:33:09.210
if you ever did this next time, then it will be your head instead of this phone. Understood?

00:33:09.410 --> 00:33:13.600
go &amp; tell your mother how pretty she looks
such disgusting people in this country

00:33:38.400 --> 00:33:40.070
you are the new receptionist

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:42.420
you've done simple graduation

00:33:42.570 --> 00:33:45.920
what is the hurry
look, how pretty you are looking

00:33:46.360 --> 00:33:48.900
and you've got no job experience as well

00:34:17.260 --> 00:34:20.110
pay the fare
I'm giving

00:34:29.020 --> 00:34:31.000
I can't find my wallet

00:34:31.190 --> 00:34:35.630
look over there... I was standing there

00:35:15.840 --> 00:35:18.080
do fry these kebabs too

00:35:18.320 --> 00:35:20.320
Ok mom

00:35:22.330 --> 00:35:23.970
greetings!

00:35:24.080 --> 00:35:26.320
greetings to you too! so what is the update

00:35:26.450 --> 00:35:28.880
any positive response or you came back like that?

00:35:29.050 --> 00:35:32.970
Kindly give me two hundred rupees, the auto rickshaw guy is waiting outside

00:35:33.450 --> 00:35:36.210
when you didn't had the money, then what was the need to use an auto rickshaw?

00:35:36.350 --> 00:35:40.050
I was helpless that is why I had used it, actually my wallet got stolen in the bus that is why

00:35:40.190 --> 00:35:44.140
this is good... you haven't earned a single penny. Hence, you've lost everything

00:35:44.330 --> 00:35:46.140
I don't have a change

00:35:46.260 --> 00:35:49.060
take from her, who is so egotistic about her salary

00:35:50.150 --> 00:35:53.000
wait, let me bring it

00:36:04.850 --> 00:36:08.470
I had a word in an office, they were saying that they are going to give me a call

00:36:08.660 --> 00:36:12.930
huh! you can pacify yourself till all these lies work out

00:36:14.180 --> 00:36:18.240
if one gets a job so easily, then there wouldn't be any poverty here

00:36:18.290 --> 00:36:21.410
and neither anyone would have died out of hunger, or would have stayed homeless

00:36:21.680 --> 00:36:25.940
and here... neither situation or fate is on our side

00:36:26.160 --> 00:36:27.940
one problem after another

00:36:28.090 --> 00:36:32.530
mom, I'm trying... it takes time to get a job

00:36:33.270 --> 00:36:35.920
right now please give me your blessings not taunts

00:36:36.040 --> 00:36:38.870
we'll see what is going to happen

00:36:41.300 --> 00:36:44.320
quickly go &amp; change your dress, there is a lot of work pending

00:36:44.530 --> 00:36:47.520
the guests will come &amp; leave after eating &amp; drinking

00:36:47.710 --> 00:36:51.530
it will be us who have to bear all the expenses in this inflation

00:37:32.590 --> 00:37:36.750
you didn't go to meet Soha?

00:37:39.280 --> 00:37:44.330
I absolutely forgot.
Today I met that Italian designer

00:37:44.700 --> 00:37:46.480
I will tell you about the meeting

00:37:52.240 --> 00:37:54.440
but you had to go to office in the morning

00:37:55.290 --> 00:37:59.960
the HR guy Zubair, today he had an argument in the factory with someone

00:38:00.330 --> 00:38:03.440
then I went there to sort out everything

00:38:10.220 --> 00:38:15.810
dear, I know you went to the factory intentionally because you doesn't want to meet Soha

00:38:16.190 --> 00:38:21.040
I had called at the factory &amp; they told me that everything was fine over there

00:38:21.710 --> 00:38:25.000
Soha kept on waiting for you at the restaurant

00:38:25.260 --> 00:38:28.390
and Mr. Imtiaz told me that...

00:38:29.270 --> 00:38:32.340
you didn't go there, and I felt so embarrassed

00:38:32.880 --> 00:38:35.430
there isn't any fault of mine in this, all is your fault

00:38:35.730 --> 00:38:40.040
I don't want to meet any of your friend's daughter
All of this was your setup

00:38:40.200 --> 00:38:44.320
Ok then tell me the name of that girl which you like

00:38:44.630 --> 00:38:47.570
Oh not again, dad! come on

00:38:47.840 --> 00:38:51.810
what is this? I've already told you that I've got no interest in the marriage

00:38:52.300 --> 00:38:55.520
but I have got a lot of interest in getting you married

00:38:55.570 --> 00:38:57.170
what is with you?

00:38:57.390 --> 00:39:02.690
why are you after one thing only?
You've been after my marriage since you got sick

00:39:04.160 --> 00:39:05.540
Basit dear look...

00:39:05.780 --> 00:39:10.110
I want you to see happy in my life

00:39:10.180 --> 00:39:16.800
that day I went to Manzoor's house, &amp; his grandson came to sit with him. He kept on playing with him

00:39:17.250 --> 00:39:21.930
by looking at him I wished to play with my grandson too

00:39:21.940 --> 00:39:24.870
what do you want!

00:39:26.870 --> 00:39:27.560
get married

00:39:27.590 --> 00:39:29.870
do you want me to do the same mistake that you did?

00:39:30.100 --> 00:39:32.180
due to which I had suffered all my life?

00:39:32.350 --> 00:39:35.290
do you want another Basit to born &amp; he shall fight with himself all his life

00:39:35.380 --> 00:39:40.580
another woman shall leave me for another man, &amp; my son shall bear the same pain that I had suffered all my life

00:39:40.640 --> 00:39:43.770
dear look, you know this very well that it was our mutual decision

00:39:43.840 --> 00:39:48.400
please! please, stop covering her infidelity

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:52.980
look... you were the most strong remembrance of this relation

00:39:53.340 --> 00:39:57.560
and I'm grateful to her that she didn't snatch you from me

00:39:57.600 --> 00:40:03.260
the favor that you are talking about was her selfishness, she ran after leaving all her responsibilities behind

00:40:03.600 --> 00:40:08.110
whatever she did... but she gave you to me

00:40:08.710 --> 00:40:11.150
I have you with me

00:40:11.520 --> 00:40:14.080
whom will you have?

00:40:14.710 --> 00:40:17.850
when I will die, then you will stay as Basit only

00:40:17.880 --> 00:40:22.530
dad please, don't say such things. Nothing will happen to you

00:40:29.210 --> 00:40:33.140
all women are not same, my dear

00:40:35.220 --> 00:40:38.690
I have seen only one woman, &amp; she was a fraudster

00:40:39.310 --> 00:40:42.660
and now I cannot trust any other woman

00:40:44.780 --> 00:40:48.640
Now we won't talk on this topic

